Cell["\<\
The fully-contracted terms processed henceforth correspond to \
fully-contracted antidiagonally-dressed disjoint Bogoliubov contributions \
generated by the application of Wick\[CloseCurlyQuote]s theorem to the \
following matrix element (cf. expansion formula of Gorkov\[CloseCurlyQuote]s \
polarization propagator), \
\>", "Text",
 CellChangeTimes->{{3.9120797623167095`*^9, 3.9120798923505526`*^9}, {
