Cell[CellGroupData[{

Cell["Input sequences of single-particle indices", "Section",
 CellChangeTimes->{{3.8874562566990304`*^9, 3.887456258704954*^9}, {
  3.8883150838482122`*^9, 
  3.8883150934469776`*^9}},ExpressionUUID->"dc3a27d2-ba94-4e6a-9f09-\
19f718534c1f"],

Cell["\<\
Loading of the 8 (4) input sequences of single particle indices, \
corresponding to antidiagonally-dressed Feynman diagrams of disjoint \
Bogoliubov type with two non-identical (identical) one-body interaction \
vertices. Contributions with non-identical vertices are twice the ones \
generated by two identical vertices, as the former do not possess any vertex \
permutation symmetry and hence have multiplicity equal to one.\
\>", "Text",
 CellChangeTimes->{{3.8883151027747664`*^9, 3.888315139028142*^9}, {
  3.888407377730768*^9, 3.888407378817301*^9}, {3.8928031069237204`*^9, 
